WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:41.837 align:middle line:90%


00:00:41.837 --> 00:00:44.170 align:middle line:84%
>> I didn't know what was
going on in my life when I was

00:00:44.170 --> 00:00:44.970 align:middle line:90%
younger.

00:00:44.970 --> 00:00:48.820 align:middle line:84%
I was kind of lost, so I just
drank as much as I could bottle

00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:50.740 align:middle line:84%
after bottle and
smoked as much weed

00:00:50.740 --> 00:00:53.080 align:middle line:84%
as I could and then
started taking acid.

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:56.740 align:middle line:84%
And at 16 years old,
I lost my girlfriend.

00:00:56.740 --> 00:00:59.500 align:middle line:84%
She overdosed on acid
and committed suicide.

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:02.950 align:middle line:84%
And then I kept going
to the point I was 21,

00:01:02.950 --> 00:01:05.080 align:middle line:84%
and I was alone in my
apartment for three days

00:01:05.080 --> 00:01:08.770 align:middle line:84%
just doing coke like
crazy, and I flatlined.

00:01:08.770 --> 00:01:11.020 align:middle line:84%
I ate a whole bag because I
thought that the cops were

00:01:11.020 --> 00:01:14.170 align:middle line:84%
coming and started hallucinating
and literally, I flatlined,

00:01:14.170 --> 00:01:16.660 align:middle line:84%
and from that point
on, I was like,

00:01:16.660 --> 00:01:19.660 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what's
happening in my life.

00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:20.530 align:middle line:90%
I don't understand.

00:01:20.530 --> 00:01:23.230 align:middle line:84%
So I quit stuff, and
I became a vegetarian.

00:01:23.230 --> 00:01:24.863 align:middle line:10%
And I'm not saying
that everybody

00:01:24.863 --> 00:01:26.530 align:middle line:10%
should be a vegetarian,
but for me, that

00:01:26.530 --> 00:01:29.183 align:middle line:10%
was the turning point
in my life because I

00:01:29.183 --> 00:01:30.850 align:middle line:10%
feel like it's the
first time in my life

00:01:30.850 --> 00:01:33.920 align:middle line:10%
where I started to be aware,
just being more aware of what I

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:34.720 align:middle line:10%
put in my body.

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:36.890 align:middle line:84%
It didn't make sense to do
a juice cleanse and then

00:01:36.890 --> 00:01:38.890 align:middle line:84%
the next day, to go to
the bar and get hammered.

00:01:38.890 --> 00:01:41.490 align:middle line:90%


00:01:41.490 --> 00:01:43.830 align:middle line:84%
And I opened a lot of
vegetarian and vegan

00:01:43.830 --> 00:01:45.540 align:middle line:90%
restaurants and vegan hotel.

00:01:45.540 --> 00:01:47.690 align:middle line:84%
And I'm having these
healthy businesses,

00:01:47.690 --> 00:01:48.960 align:middle line:90%
and I'm trying to help people.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:50.590 align:middle line:90%
And I don't do drugs anymore.

00:01:50.590 --> 00:01:51.390 align:middle line:90%
I don't do this.

00:01:51.390 --> 00:01:52.190 align:middle line:90%
I don't do that.

00:01:52.190 --> 00:01:54.580 align:middle line:90%
And I did all this other stuff.

00:01:54.580 --> 00:01:56.770 align:middle line:84%
And I felt like I kind
of got addicted to work.

00:01:56.770 --> 00:01:58.800 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we can do
everything that way,

00:01:58.800 --> 00:02:00.750 align:middle line:84%
probably little drama
still because he's

00:02:00.750 --> 00:02:02.042 align:middle line:90%
friends with some of the staff.

00:02:02.042 --> 00:02:04.250 align:middle line:84%
So that's stuff that we'll
always deal with probably,

00:02:04.250 --> 00:02:05.250 align:middle line:90%
no matter what.

00:02:05.250 --> 00:02:06.780 align:middle line:90%
What happens after she signs it?

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:07.980 align:middle line:90%
Because she told me--

00:02:07.980 --> 00:02:09.105 align:middle line:90%
I haven't written her back.

00:02:09.105 --> 00:02:10.979 align:middle line:84%
So I stopped those
other things, and I

00:02:10.979 --> 00:02:13.710 align:middle line:84%
started working like crazy
amounts and became successful.

00:02:13.710 --> 00:02:16.260 align:middle line:84%
And I was still waking up
in the middle of the night

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:19.140 align:middle line:84%
and going to the emergency room
because my heart was skipping

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:22.860 align:middle line:84%
beats, and I was having
full-blown anxiety and panic

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:24.830 align:middle line:90%
attacks.

00:02:24.830 --> 00:02:25.630 align:middle line:90%
Anxiety.

00:02:25.630 --> 00:02:26.770 align:middle line:90%
My face is tingling.

00:02:26.770 --> 00:02:35.758 align:middle line:90%


00:02:35.758 --> 00:02:37.550 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't understand
what was happening.

00:02:37.550 --> 00:02:39.300 align:middle line:84%
I would wake up in the
middle of the night

00:02:39.300 --> 00:02:43.400 align:middle line:84%
sometimes and feel this
fear taking over me

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:45.380 align:middle line:84%
to the point where my
heart was skipping beats,

00:02:45.380 --> 00:02:47.990 align:middle line:84%
and I couldn't even speak
because my face was getting

00:02:47.990 --> 00:02:52.130 align:middle line:84%
so tingly and numb, and my whole
body was kind of tightening up.

00:02:52.130 --> 00:02:54.490 align:middle line:84%
And I don't know, I
felt like I was dying.

00:02:54.490 --> 00:02:58.912 align:middle line:90%


00:02:58.912 --> 00:03:00.620 align:middle line:10%
And then that's how
this journey started.

00:03:00.620 --> 00:03:06.620 align:middle line:90%


00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:11.130 align:middle line:10%
I was super confused because
I had all this fear in me,

00:03:11.130 --> 00:03:14.540 align:middle line:10%
but on the other hand, I was
totally secure in terms of what

00:03:14.540 --> 00:03:15.770 align:middle line:10%
the world kind of taught me.

00:03:15.770 --> 00:03:16.570 align:middle line:10%
I was secure.

00:03:16.570 --> 00:03:19.480 align:middle line:10%
I had a house and good
job and was making money.

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:20.480 align:middle line:10%
So it didn't make sense.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.313 align:middle line:10%
I didn't really understand
what the hell was

00:03:22.313 --> 00:03:25.040 align:middle line:10%
going on to feel these
things and to have everything

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:28.870 align:middle line:10%
that I thought that I
was supposed to have.

00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:31.630 align:middle line:10%
So we've been traveling around
the world for the last two

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:34.330 align:middle line:10%
years with the
effort of me really

00:03:34.330 --> 00:03:36.887 align:middle line:10%
understanding who I am better.

00:03:36.887 --> 00:03:38.720 align:middle line:10%
But for me, it was a
very challenging thing,

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:40.100 align:middle line:10%
and it still is.

00:03:40.100 --> 00:03:42.540 align:middle line:10%
It takes focus, and
it takes dedication,

00:03:42.540 --> 00:03:44.840 align:middle line:10%
and it takes a really
strong will to do it.

