00:08:13.100 --> 00:08:14.840 align:middle line:84%
>> As I say pretty
much every week,

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:23.420 align:middle line:84%
we are a social species and that
our biggest core drive in life

00:08:23.420 --> 00:08:27.110 align:middle line:84%
