established by looking

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.670 align:middle line:90%
into the eye of someone--

00:08:58.670 --> 00:09:01.430 align:middle line:84%
your parents, your
caregivers, the other adults--

00:09:01.430 --> 00:09:05.420 align:middle line:84%
