express whatever state you're

00:09:05.420 --> 00:09:07.460 align:middle line:90%
in through your emotions.

00:09:07.460 --> 00:09:10.730 align:middle line:84%
So you're tired, you're
frustrated, you're sad,

00:09:10.730 --> 00:09:12.110 align:middle line:84%
you're lonely,
you're vulnerable,

00:09:12.110 --> 00:09:15.890 align:middle line:84%
you express that
physiologically.

00:09:15.890 --> 00:09:21.070 align:middle line:84%
Those times where we feel
disconnected from care,

00:09:21.070 --> 00:09:25.600 align:middle line:84%
