00:50:40.690 --> 00:50:42.100 align:middle line:90%
or tomorrow.

00:50:42.100 --> 00:50:44.890 align:middle line:84%
That's a different
thought from, oh my god,

00:50:44.890 --> 00:50:46.848 align:middle line:90%
this is a horrible fiasco.

00:50:46.848 --> 00:50:47.890 align:middle line:90%
This is a terrible thing.

00:50:47.890 --> 00:50:50.530 align:middle line:90%
My business is failing.

00:50:50.530 --> 00:50:52.580 align:middle line:90%
Those feel differently.

00:50:52.580 --> 00:50:54.460 align:middle line:84%
>> So are those
thoughts the suffering?

00:50:54.460 --> 00:50:55.940 align:middle line:84%
The ones that
