00:50:55.940 --> 00:50:56.740 align:middle line:90%
Is that--

00:50:56.740 --> 00:50:57.010 align:middle line:90%
>> That's it.

00:50:57.010 --> 00:50:58.240 align:middle line:84%
>> --maybe your
definition of suffering?

00:50:58.240 --> 00:50:59.470 align:middle line:90%
>> That's it.

00:50:59.470 --> 00:51:01.270 align:middle line:84%
If these kind of
thoughts are quiet,

00:51:01.270 --> 00:51:03.280 align:middle line:84%
and most people, 99%
of their thoughts

00:51:03.280 --> 00:51:06.070 align:middle line:84%
