thoughts, the bad thoughts,

00:51:06.070 --> 00:51:08.440 align:middle line:84%
and so if you can
quiet those down,

00:51:08.440 --> 00:51:11.450 align:middle line:84%
you gain a huge
amount of bandwidth.

00:51:11.450 --> 00:51:13.250 align:middle line:90%
The whole thing is--

00:51:13.250 --> 00:51:15.350 align:middle line:84%
now, this thing
