00:51:15.350 --> 00:51:16.760 align:middle line:90%
There's just nothing going on.

00:51:16.760 --> 00:51:18.110 align:middle line:90%
It's just quiet.

00:51:18.110 --> 00:51:21.620 align:middle line:84%
