00:51:24.472 --> 00:51:26.180 align:middle line:84%
all the things that
you're talking about?

00:51:26.180 --> 00:51:27.050 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:51:27.050 --> 00:51:29.740 align:middle line:84%
>> So you don't feel like
