00:51:43.996 --> 00:51:45.950 align:middle line:90%
You watch your thoughts.

00:51:45.950 --> 00:51:47.270 align:middle line:90%
You could watch your thoughts.

00:51:47.270 --> 00:51:48.860 align:middle line:84%
You could see all
that taking place.

00:51:48.860 --> 00:51:50.780 align:middle line:90%
They all had an I in them.

00:51:50.780 --> 00:51:53.540 align:middle line:84%
Part of this stuff that
I do, this practice,

00:51:53.540 --> 00:51:55.070 align:middle line:84%
is getting rid of
your attachments

00:51:55.070 --> 00:51:58.400 align:middle line:84%
because the attachments
really generate the I.

00:51:58.400 --> 00:51:59.250 align:middle line:90%
They work together.

00:51:59.250 --> 00:52:01.362 align:middle line:90%
I want this green tea.

00:52:01.362 --> 00:52:02.570 align:middle line:90%
I have to have the green tea.

00:52:02.570 --> 00:52:05.300 align:middle line:84%
If I don't, oh my
gosh, it got terrible.

00:52:05.300 --> 00:52:08.750 align:middle line:84%
So you just deconstruct
all those attachments.

00:52:08.750 --> 00:52:11.690 align:middle line:84%
And so that drives you
forward because as you

00:52:11.690 --> 00:52:15.860 align:middle line:84%
start to take apart James,
you find a lot of resistance.

00:52:15.860 --> 00:52:18.380 align:middle line:84%
