about this and that,

00:52:18.380 --> 00:52:20.750 align:middle line:84%
a lot of old memories,
a lot of old traumas,

00:52:20.750 --> 00:52:24.710 align:middle line:84%
and there's ways to push through
those, to look at them and say,

00:52:24.710 --> 00:52:26.720 align:middle line:90%
where's the James in this one?

00:52:26.720 --> 00:52:29.570 align:middle line:84%
You look at your attachments
and what's attachment to that.

00:52:29.570 --> 00:52:33.080 align:middle line:84%
There's a James there attached
to the car or the reputation

00:52:33.080 --> 00:52:35.870 align:middle line:84%
