00:52:37.490 --> 00:52:40.550 align:middle line:84%
You can break all
those down, but you've

00:52:40.550 --> 00:52:43.172 align:middle line:84%
got to decide, hey,
this is serious.

00:52:43.172 --> 00:52:45.380 align:middle line:84%
I can't just buy another
car, get another girlfriend,

00:52:45.380 --> 00:52:46.850 align:middle line:90%
