00:53:10.480 --> 00:53:12.490 align:middle line:90%
I don't want to suffer anymore.

00:53:12.490 --> 00:53:14.100 align:middle line:90%
I'm done suffering.

00:53:14.100 --> 00:53:15.540 align:middle line:90%
This has to stop.

